commits.author: Adrien Grand
commits.sourceNew: /** * Read iterations * blockCount() blocks from blocks, * decode them and write iterations * valueCount() values into * values. * * @param blocks the long blocks that hold packed integer values * @param blocksOffset the offset where to start reading blocks * @param values the values buffer * @param valuesOffset the offset where to start writing values * @param iterations controls how much data to decode */ void decode(long[] blocks, int blocksOffset, long[] values, int valuesOffset, int iterations);
